Description: Tools for AI-assisted qualitative data annotation using large language
    models (LLMs). Provides predefined tasks for sentiment analysis, stance
    detection, ideological scaling, topic salience, and fact-checking, as well as
    custom task definitions. Includes functions for computing intercoder
    reliability and gold-standard validation metrics, reproducible annotation
    trails across multiple LLM configurations, and an interactive 'shiny'
    application for manual coding and LLM output validation.
